'''Malab''' was a smooth and highly reflective black mineral found only on [[Telos IV]]. Lighting a [[Glowrod/Legends|glow rod]] in a cave of malab would give the illusion of standing beneath thousands of [[Star/Legends|stars]]. Due to its rarity and natural beauty, it was highly prized throughout [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]].

During the [[Dark Jedi/Legends|Dark Jedi]] [[Xanatos]]' control of Telos IV, malab was one of the natural resources harvested by Xanatos' [[Offworld Mining Corporation]]. For [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] and [[Qui-Gon Jinn/Legends|Qui-Gon Jinn]], it served as evidence of Xanatos' manipulation of the Telosian population.

